            "enable_switches": false,
            "enable_all_collection": false,
            "title": "What if I spill liquid on it?",
            "text": "<p>Disconnect power immediately. Air dry upside down for 48+ hours. Avoid high heat. Ensure it's completely dry before powering on.</p>"
